    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>I found myself shaking my head in disgust while reading about the self-involved socialites seeking to make green the new Prada.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>I found myself shaking my head in disgust while reading about the self-involved socialites seeking to make green the new Prada.</p>
        <p>If Sloan Barnett, the party's hostess, wants to do something to help the earth, she should start by trading her five-story town house for something more appropriate for her family. She could save a bundle on cleaning supplies.</p>
        <p>Aaron Berger  Minneapolis</p>
      </block>
